\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Simply point your camera at any meal or food item. Our computer vision model identifies ingredients in real-time, matches them against our nutrition database of 900,000+ foods, and calculates precise macros — protein, fats, carbs, and calories.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Does Enerium sync with Apple Health and Google Fit?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Yes. Enerium deeply integrates with Apple HealthKit and Google Fit. Steps, workouts, active minutes, and body metrics sync automatically in both directions.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Can I use Enerium for meal planning?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Absolutely. Our AI generates a complete weekly meal plan tailored to your calorie goals, dietary preferences, and the ingredients you already have at home. Each plan includes a ready-to-use shopping list.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"What is the Smart Fridge feature?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Smart Fridge lets you manage a virtual inventory of your real fridge and pantry. The AI then suggests recipes based on what you have, helping you reduce food waste and eat better without extra shopping.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Is my health data private and secure?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Your privacy is our top priority. All health data is encrypted end-to-end and stored securely. We never sell your data to third parties. You can export or delete your data at any time.\\\"}}]},{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ItemList\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Enerium App Features\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Five health dimensions powered by AI in the Enerium app\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Nutrition Intelligence\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Track every calorie and macro with precision. AI-powered food recognition analyzes your meals instantly from a single photo.\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Fitness \\u0026 Activity\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Steps, workouts, runs, training videos, and multi-week marathon programs. Synced with Apple Health and Google Fit.\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Smart Hydration\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Intelligent water tracking with adaptive reminders that escalate based on urgency. Never forget to hydrate.\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":4,\\\"name\\\":\\\"AI Kitchen\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Smart fridge inventory, AI recipe suggestions from your ingredients, automatic meal planning, and shopping lists.\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":5,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Deep Analytics\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Comprehensive progress tracking with custom date ranges, trend analysis, body metrics, and exportable insights.\\\"}]}]}\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"12:T5a1,{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@graph\\\":[{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Enerium\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://enerium.app\\\",\\\"logo\\\":\\\"https://enerium.app/logo.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"AI-powered health app for nutrition tracking, meal planning, hydration reminders, fitness syncing, and wellness analytics in one platform.\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"hello@enerium.app\\\",\\\"contactPoint\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ContactPoint\\\",\\\"contactType\\\":\\\"customer support\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"hello@enerium.app\\\",\\\"availableLanguage\\\":[\\\"en\\\"]},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ContactPoint\\\",\\\"contactType\\\":\\\"privacy support\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"privacy@enerium.app\\\",\\\"availableLanguage\\\":[\\\"en\\\"]},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Contact